#, kde-format
msgctxt "technical term, do you have a musician friend?"
msgid "Practice recognizing seventh chords built with a minor seventh by ear."
msgstr "Вправляння у розпізнаванні септими з мінорним сьомим на слух."

#, kde-format
msgctxt "technical term, do you have a musician friend?"
msgid "Practice recognizing seventh chords with flattened or sharpened fifths."
msgstr ""
"Вправляння у розпізнаванні семерних акордів зі сплюченими або загостреними "
"квінтами."

#, kde-format
msgctxt "technical term, do you have a musician friend?"
msgid ""
"Practice recognizing symmetric scale sounds such as whole-tone and "
"diminished patterns."
